ConditionOnsetdateSearchParameter

Parameter onset-date:date

Searches for condition based on the condition onset date concept eg) /ws/fhir2/{release}/Condition?onset-date={date}

ResourceCondition
Expression(none)
Target ResourcesCondition
MultiplesThe parameter cannot repeat or have multiple values
